Package models

Class WithdrawalRequest

java.lang.Object
models.WithdrawalRequest
public class WithdrawalRequest extends Object
Represents a withdrawal request for a BTO application. Contains information about the withdrawal request including its status, the related application, and processing details.

      Parameters:
      requestId - the unique ID of the withdrawal request
      applicationId - the associated application ID
      applicantNric - the NRIC of the applicant making the request
      projectName - the project name related to the withdrawal request
      status - the status of the request
      requestDate - the date and time when the request was made
      processDate - the date and time when the request was processed
      remarks - any additional remarks regarding the request
